"{\n  \"judgement\": \"The argument that faith and prayer can be a valid means of connection with a higher power, despite lack of empirical evidence, is more defensible than dismissing it outright as a form of emotional manipulation.\",\n  \"steering\": \"It's interesting to see how people's experiences with spirituality and faith can vary so greatly. Maybe we can learn from each other's perspectives and find common ground, even if we don't all agree on the same things?\"}"